main event: A report was generated regarding a UFO observation in Kelso, Washington on July 23, 1955, attributed to the presence of satellites.
interesting points: The sighting involved one object observed visually from the ground., The object was observed moving south., The Air Force was unable to specifically identify the satellite observed., The report references multiple satellites being visible to the naked eye., The document is part of Project Blue Book, an official U.S. Air Force investigation.
